&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; page-break-before: always;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Segunda-Parte&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1 - O &amp;quot;Jeitinho&amp;quot; Digital Brasileiro: &amp;quot;Gambiarras&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Mutir&amp;otilde;es&amp;quot; e &amp;quot;Puxadinhos&amp;quot;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;(No Brasil) temos uma tradi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o antropof&amp;aacute;gica que &amp;eacute; totalmente coerente com a cultura &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;hacker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;, combinando elementos de origens diferentes em produtos criativos. Somos historicamente perif&amp;eacute;ricos (...) Aqui, a colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; sempre uma estrat&amp;eacute;gia de sobreviv&amp;ecirc;ncia. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;- Hernani Dimantas, &amp;quot;Linkania - A Multid&amp;atilde;o Conectada&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Os media t&amp;aacute;cticos s&amp;atilde;o o mais recente invasor a ser consumido pelos jovens canibais gentis do Brasil&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;- David Garcia, &amp;quot;Fine Young Cannibals, of Brazilian Tactical Media&amp;quot; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Iniciativas como o Projecto Met&amp;aacute;fora e o seu descendente Metareciclagem n&amp;atilde;o surgiram isoladamente, desligadas do contexto local. Antes pelo contr&amp;aacute;rio, elas s&amp;atilde;o fruto do seu meio ambiente. Apesar de as destacarmos nesta investiga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, elas nasceram no mesmo per&amp;iacute;odo - durante os primeiros anos do s&amp;eacute;culo XXI - que outros colectivos brasileiros actuando com as tecnologias medi&amp;aacute;ticas mais simples e acess&amp;iacute;veis para fins de activismo pol&amp;iacute;tico, cr&amp;iacute;tica dos media comerciais ou inclus&amp;atilde;o social. Quer se considerassem a si pr&amp;oacute;prios media t&amp;aacute;cticos, quer ignorassem que o que estavam a fazer tinha esse nome, esses grupos partilharam desde o in&amp;iacute;cio uma l&amp;oacute;gica criativa e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Do-It-Yourself. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Este movimento de colectivos que ocupa uma posi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o marginal face ao sistema art&amp;iacute;stico e discurso pol&amp;iacute;tico dominantes foi caracterizado pelo te&amp;oacute;rico dos media Ricardo Rosas de Vingan&amp;ccedil;a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Low-Tech&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote1sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote1anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt; (Rosas, 2004), uma vingan&amp;ccedil;a &amp;quot;contra a elite tecno-fetichista, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;high-tech&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt; e auto-indulgente dos Web-artistas no Brasil que se interessa apenas com o seu ego&amp;iacute;smo obsessivo&amp;quot;. Uma vez que grande parte da popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o n&amp;atilde;o tem acesso &amp;agrave;s mais recentes tecnologias de ponta do modo como o circuito da arte e as grandes empresas disp&amp;otilde;em, a melhor maneira de se lhes opor consiste em tirar partido das ferramentas dispon&amp;iacute;veis. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Apesar do m&amp;eacute;todo destes grupos assentar no recurso a tecnologia acess&amp;iacute;vel para produzir ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e trabalhos no espa&amp;ccedil;o f&amp;iacute;sico, eles mant&amp;ecirc;m interliga&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e colaboram entre si atrav&amp;eacute;s de comunidades virtuais na Internet. Segundo Karla Brunet, &amp;quot;s&amp;atilde;o projectos de oposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o n&amp;atilde;o s&amp;oacute; ao poder, mas que tamb&amp;eacute;m criam um novo poder na Net&amp;quot; (Brunet, 2005) e, nesse aspecto, diferenciam-se  de outras pr&amp;aacute;ticas t&amp;aacute;cticas dominantes em zonas mais centrais como a Europa e a Am&amp;eacute;rica do Norte. Tendo em conta o contexto nacional, dedicam uma aten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o especial &amp;agrave; inclus&amp;atilde;o digital e &amp;agrave; educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. O seu objectivo n&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute;, por isso, apenas disponibilizar um maior acesso &amp;agrave; Internet e a outras tecnologias digitais, mas tamb&amp;eacute;m a promo&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o cr&amp;iacute;tica e criativa dos media atrav&amp;eacute;s de &amp;quot;diversas formas e padr&amp;otilde;es de modo a que se transformem em algo novo, experimental e criando ocasionalmente ru&amp;iacute;do e dist&amp;uacute;rbios&amp;quot; (&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;). Estes projectos visam assim adaptar o conceito de media t&amp;aacute;cticos &amp;agrave; realidade de um pa&amp;iacute;s de graves contrastes sociais e econ&amp;oacute;micos como o Brasil, onde a maioria da popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o n&amp;atilde;o tem acesso &amp;agrave; educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, sa&amp;uacute;de e habita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pr&amp;oacute;pria e o sector dos media &amp;eacute; dominado por grandes conglomerados multim&amp;eacute;dia como a Globo e a Abril. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ricardo Rosas acusa estes gigantes de &amp;quot;representarem os interesses da elite e de tentarem manter a apar&amp;ecirc;ncia de um consenso complacente, mesmo face a conflitos sociais intensos&amp;quot;. Na sua opini&amp;atilde;o, a sociedade brasileira encontra-se submersa num consenso mediatizado formado pelas telenovelas e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;reality-shows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;, o que faz com que os pontos de vista cr&amp;iacute;ticos tendem a ser escassos e bastante marginais (Rosas, 2004). Se olharmos para o caso da esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o televisiva Globo, por exemplo, podemos verificar o poder desta influ&amp;ecirc;ncia na popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o quando verificamos que, para al&amp;eacute;m de ser um dos maiores conglomerados de media do mundo, &amp;eacute; o maior produtor privado de programas em todo o mundo (Wells, 2005). Como refere David Garcia, &amp;quot;tal como o imp&amp;eacute;rio de Berlusconi, a Globo vai muito para al&amp;eacute;m da televis&amp;atilde;o: ela abarca todos os media poss&amp;iacute;veis, incluindo a imprensa&amp;quot;, dispondo assim do poder de &amp;quot;determinar os resultados de elei&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e de influenciar importantes decis&amp;otilde;es pol&amp;iacute;ticas num curto espa&amp;ccedil;o de tempo&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote2sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote2anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt; (Garcia, 2004a). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Em resposta, alguns colectivos surgidos no in&amp;iacute;cio deste s&amp;eacute;culo pretendem constituir uma forma de ant&amp;iacute;doto destinada a curar &amp;quot;uma sociedade mediatizada de uma natureza particularmente virulenta&amp;quot; como a brasileira &amp;quot;em que vastas hordas da popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o s&amp;atilde;o literalmente anestesiadas pela dieta de telenovelas da Globo&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;idem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;). Trata-se de transformar os espectadores em protagonistas que n&amp;atilde;o se limitem a criticar e a reagir aos media a partir da posi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o passiva que ocupam quando apenas mudam de canal com o comando. Para tal, consideram necess&amp;aacute;rio um &amp;quot;Vietcongue dos media&amp;quot;, nas palavras do artista gr&amp;aacute;fico Latuff, citado por Garcia, atrav&amp;eacute;s do qual as pessoas possam recriar a sua pr&amp;oacute;pria realidade mediante a produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos seus pr&amp;oacute;prios media e que transforme radicalmente as estruturas existentes da propriedade e utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos media electr&amp;oacute;nicos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote3sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote3anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ibidem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;).  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.1 - M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Foi com base nesta filosofia de ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de questionamento do monop&amp;oacute;lio medi&amp;aacute;tico dos conglomerados multim&amp;eacute;dia que Ricardo Rosas e as artistas Tatiana Wells e Giselli Vasconcelos organizaram em Mar&amp;ccedil;o de 2003 na cidade de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo o festival M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica Brasil&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote4sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote4anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;, um laborat&amp;oacute;rio de media t&amp;aacute;cticos que decorreu no edif&amp;iacute;cio Casa das Rosas, situado na Avenida Paulista - o centro financeiro e econ&amp;oacute;mico da cidade -, que consistiu numa vers&amp;atilde;o brasileira do Next Five Minutes de Amesterd&amp;atilde;o, realizado a par de outros eventos semelhantes que tiveram lugar em v&amp;aacute;rias partes do mundo ao longo desse ano. Apesar do or&amp;ccedil;amento bastante limitado, o festival atraiu cerca de quatro mil visitantes e uma enorme cobertura medi&amp;aacute;tica. Sobretudo, devido &amp;agrave; presen&amp;ccedil;a do Ministro da Cultura e cantor Gilberto Gil &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;   &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Entre os colectivos intervenientes, para al&amp;eacute;m do Met&amp;aacute;fora, participaram videoactivistas com motiva&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es pol&amp;iacute;ticas - A Revolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o N&amp;atilde;o Ser&amp;aacute; Televisionada e Bijari&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote5sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote5anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;5&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; -, grupos de ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o directa e interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o urbana &amp;ndash; Batuka&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, Rejeitados e Bicicletadas -, iniciativas dedicadas &amp;agrave; cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de farsas e par&amp;oacute;dias - Projecto Sid Moreira - produtores de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;fanzines&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; - A Cria -, revistas destinadas ao apoio dos sem-abrigo &amp;ndash; Ocas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote6sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote6anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;6&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; -,  um colectivo de DJs que realiza &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;raves&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; gratuitas nos sub&amp;uacute;rbios &amp;ndash; Interfusion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote7sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote7anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;7&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; -, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;artistas com trabalhos de interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o nos media &amp;ndash; Latuff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote8sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote8anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;8&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e Formigueiro -, uma r&amp;aacute;dio livre - R&amp;aacute;dio Muda&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote9sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote9anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;9&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; -, e um grupo que recolhe narrativas individuais de an&amp;oacute;nimos em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo &amp;ndash; Museu da Pessoa&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote10sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote10anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;10&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Embora uma parte importante destes colectivos fossem origin&amp;aacute;rios de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, muitos estavam espalhados por outras grandes cidades do pa&amp;iacute;s. Como explica Ricardo Rosas, &amp;quot;havia tanta diferen&amp;ccedil;a e diversidade entre os diferentes grupos que parecia, por vezes, que as suas pr&amp;aacute;ticas eram contradit&amp;oacute;rias entre si.&amp;quot; (Rosas, 2004). O evento congregou durante quatro dias te&amp;oacute;ricos, activistas e artistas brasileiros e estrangeiros e o seu programa abarcou apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es dos colectivos, debates, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, confer&amp;ecirc;ncias, uma exposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, espect&amp;aacute;culos musicais, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;performances&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, festas espont&amp;acirc;neas e &amp;quot;uma esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o tempor&amp;aacute;ria de r&amp;aacute;dio pirata que desafiou as pol&amp;iacute;ticas repressivas em rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;agrave;s emissoras livres no Brasil&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem), &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;a r&amp;aacute;dio &amp;quot;Pega Eu&amp;quot;, que iremos referir mais &amp;agrave; frente neste cap&amp;iacute;tulo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Impressionados com o &amp;ecirc;xito do primeiro laborat&amp;oacute;rio de media t&amp;aacute;cticos no Brasil, os tr&amp;ecirc;s organizadores decidiram expandir o conceito M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica e estabelecer um movimento com o mesmo nome visando funcionar como uma rede de media t&amp;aacute;cticos que facilitasse a comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e a colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com outros grupos desenvolvendo trabalhos na &amp;agrave;rea de intersec&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre a arte, os media e a tecnologia (Wells, 2005). O M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote11sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote11anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;11&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; funciona como uma plataforma simultaneamente &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;offline&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; que organiza e apoia a cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de ambientes comuns - como festivais, publica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, sites ou laborat&amp;oacute;rios tempor&amp;aacute;rios - em que estes colectivos independentes e aut&amp;oacute;nomos se podem reunir e trocar ideias e experi&amp;ecirc;ncias. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Esta rede de parcerias foi implementada pela primeira vez na pr&amp;aacute;tica nas favelas e sub&amp;uacute;rbios de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, atrav&amp;eacute;s do projecto Autolabs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote12sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote12anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;12&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; iniciado em Fevereiro de 2004. Os Autolabs constituem &amp;quot;laborat&amp;oacute;rios de literacia dos media, experimenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o tecnol&amp;oacute;gica e criatividade desenvolvidos com o apoio das comunidades locais&amp;quot;, de acordo com Ricardo Rosas (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;2004&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). Empregando &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre e outros media &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;DIY&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; acess&amp;iacute;veis, estes laborat&amp;oacute;rios ensinam os princ&amp;iacute;pios, conceitos e pr&amp;aacute;ticas t&amp;aacute;cticas de forma a incentivar a produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o cultural independente. A aprendizagem &amp;eacute; aqui realizada de um modo colaborativo e em rede, incidindo na utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e dom&amp;iacute;nio de ferramentas de produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o gr&amp;aacute;fica, sonora - r&amp;aacute;dios livres, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;VJing&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;DJing&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; -, v&amp;iacute;deo - televis&amp;atilde;o pirata  - e direccionada para a Web por parte de jovens que normalmente n&amp;atilde;o disp&amp;otilde;em dos recursos que o acesso &amp;agrave;s tecnologias de comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o exige. Este tipo de zonas tempor&amp;aacute;rias aut&amp;oacute;nomas s&amp;atilde;o fruto de parcerias estabelecidas entre iniciativas sociais aut&amp;oacute;nomas como o Metareciclagem, o CMI-Brasil, o Colectivo de Hist&amp;oacute;rias Digitais&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote13sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote13anc&quot; class=&quo