&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Em Julho de 2004, no final do projecto, tinham sido implementados tr&amp;ecirc;s centros de media em S&amp;atilde;o Miguel Paulista, Ermelino Matarazzo e Itaquera, bairros da zona leste de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo. O projecto foi parcialmente financiado atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma bolsa atribu&amp;iacute;da pela Unesco e resultou de uma alian&amp;ccedil;a com a organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o n&amp;atilde;o-governamental La Fabbrica - ligada ao grupo italiano Fiat -, por interm&amp;eacute;dio de um projecto de ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o social denominado CAJU (Centro de Ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o Juvenil). Outro apoio inesperado foi o da autarquia local, atrav&amp;eacute;s da sua ag&amp;ecirc;ncia de tecnologia Governo Electr&amp;oacute;nico. Esta institui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o tem vindo a desenvolver ao longo dos &amp;uacute;ltimos anos v&amp;aacute;rias iniciativas de combate &amp;agrave; divis&amp;atilde;o digital, sendo uma das mais importantes os Telecentros&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote15sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote15anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;15&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, isto &amp;eacute;, centros de acesso p&amp;uacute;blico &amp;agrave; Internet com computadores correndo Linux e outro &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;software&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote16sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote16anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;16&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;ndash; e. Juntamente com o Prodam, empresa municipal especializada na disponibiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de infra-estrutura tecnol&amp;oacute;gica, forneceu uma liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o em banda larga r&amp;aacute;pida &amp;agrave; Internet. Depois do fim dos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, os laborat&amp;oacute;rios foram integrados na rede de Telecentros e alguns dos jovens que receberam forma&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o foram empregues como monitores dos centro p&amp;uacute;blicos. Ali&amp;aacute;s, &amp;eacute; importante frisar que os Autolabs surgiram em parte como reac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e cr&amp;iacute;tica aos Telecentros. Como Garcia coloca a quest&amp;atilde;o: &amp;quot;O que &amp;eacute; que importa que os computadores corram Linux se os visitantes apenas utilizam os servi&amp;ccedil;os de mensagens e navegam e  m sites de pornografia ou da Globo?&amp;quot; (Garcia, 2004a). Os organizadores dos Autolabs consideram que os Telecentros se baseiam numa cren&amp;ccedil;a err&amp;oacute;nea no poder da informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, s&amp;oacute; por si, desencadear transforma&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sociais, acabando por oferecer pouco mais do que acesso &amp;agrave; Net. Na medida em que s&amp;atilde;o um instrumento de &amp;quot;inclus&amp;atilde;o digital&amp;quot;, os Telecentros s&amp;atilde;o vistos por activistas como Rosas como um exemplo de uma pol&amp;iacute;tica estabelecida de cima para baixo e unidireccional pelo Estado que se limita a oferecer acesso &amp;agrave;s tecnologias digitais &amp;agrave;queles que n&amp;atilde;o possuem computadores, acabando por &amp;quot;reflectir o mesmo &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;ethos&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de desigualdade e hierarquia que aparentemente se prop&amp;otilde;e a desafiar&amp;quot; (Rosas, 2004). As pr&amp;aacute;ticas e utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es di&amp;aacute;rias, assim como as necessidades das comunidades visadas s&amp;atilde;o ignoradas, &amp;quot;dando mais &amp;ecirc;nfase ao consumo do que &amp;agrave; produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o cr&amp;iacute;tica e criativa&amp;quot;. Para Ricardo Rosas, &amp;quot;esta pol&amp;iacute;tica tenta responder &amp;agrave;s consequ&amp;ecirc;ncias e n&amp;atilde;o &amp;agrave;s causas da realidade em que procura intervir&amp;quot;, e &amp;quot;cria frequentemente mais problemas do que soluciona&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote17sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote17anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;17&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. N&amp;atilde;o admira por isso que alguns dos envolvidos nos Autolabs considerem que a recente liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com o poder pol&amp;iacute;tico atrav&amp;eacute;s da integra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o nos Telecentros compromete os objectivos iniciais de autonomia e independ&amp;ecirc;ncia (Garcia, 2004a). Por outro lado, David Garcia indica que o modelo cr&amp;iacute;tico de educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o para os media, produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o medi&amp;aacute;tica e reciclagem de computadores presente nos Autolabs tem sido levado em conta nos mais recentes projectos de inclus&amp;atilde;o digital desenvolvidos pelo Minist&amp;eacute;rio da Cultura (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). Ricardo Rosas nota que os novos Telecentros h&amp;iacute;bridos s&amp;atilde;o bastante diferentes do prot&amp;oacute;tipo original, no sentido em que combinam a inten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de autonomia e liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;agrave;s comunidades presente nos Autolabs. Falando em termos metaf&amp;oacute;ricos, Rosas v&amp;ecirc; os Autolabs como &amp;quot;um conceito &#039;alien&amp;iacute;gena&#039; vivendo dentro do corpo uma pol&amp;iacute;tica &#039;hospedeira&#039;, a&amp;iacute; implementado uma forma de &#039;subvers&amp;atilde;o pr&amp;aacute;tica&#039; ao mesmo tempo que s&amp;atilde;o financiados e apoiados por grandes institui&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es&amp;quot; (Rosas, 2004)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote18sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote18anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;18&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Apesar da desconfian&amp;ccedil;a inicial, a rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre os colectivos de base e o governo tem-se estendido a todo o sector do movimento do &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre e das utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sociais das novas tecnologias. Para al&amp;eacute;m de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, centenas de Telecentros foram tamb&amp;eacute;m sendo introduzidos noutras cidades brasileiras controladas pelo Partido dos Trabalhadores (PT) - que ocupa actualmente o governo -, de modo a permitir uma inclus&amp;atilde;o digital da popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos bairros mais carenciados, atrav&amp;eacute;s da utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre. Com a ascens&amp;atilde;o de Lula da Silva &amp;agrave; presid&amp;ecirc;ncia, os Telecentros passaram de experi&amp;ecirc;ncias locais a iniciativas federais&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote19sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote19anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;19&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Um dos coordenadores desta iniciativa &amp;eacute; Cla&amp;uacute;dio Prado. Enquanto respons&amp;aacute;vel pelas pol&amp;iacute;ticas digitais do Minist&amp;eacute;rio da Cultura, Prado foi tamb&amp;eacute;m o arquitecto de uma experi&amp;ecirc;ncia semelhante, as BACs (Bases de Apoio &amp;agrave; Cultura), que &amp;quot;previa cerca de cinquenta mega-centros de cultura digital em comunidades perif&amp;eacute;ricas em todo o Brasil, com est&amp;uacute;dios de produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o multim&amp;eacute;dia e uma grande infra-estrutura tecnol&amp;oacute;gica integrando todos eles&amp;quot; (Fonseca, 2005)&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote20sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote20anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;20&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Este projecto foi, no entanto, substitu&amp;iacute;do pelos Pontos de Cultura, inserido na estrat&amp;eacute;gia Cultura Viva&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote21sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote21anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;21&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; do Minist&amp;eacute;rio que prev&amp;ecirc; o desenvolvimento de mil centros multim&amp;eacute;dia espalhados pelo pa&amp;iacute;s e baseados nos princ&amp;iacute;pios da colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e autonomia, visando potenciar a democratiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o cultural. Para al&amp;eacute;m do Midia T&amp;aacute;tica, o MetaReciclagem &amp;eacute;, como veremos mais &amp;agrave; frente em pormenor, um dos colectivos que est&amp;aacute; ligado aos Pontos de Cultura, sendo que alguns dos seus elementos que come&amp;ccedil;aram por desenvolver trabalho volunt&amp;aacute;rio a&amp;iacute; foram entretanto integrados como funcion&amp;aacute;rios do Minist&amp;eacute;rio da Cultura. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;O evento seguinte organizado pelos elementos do M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica foi o festival Digitofagia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote22sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote22anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;22&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, que teve lugar em Outubro de 2004  em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo e no Rio de Janeiro, que reuniu activistas, te&amp;oacute;ricos e artistas nacionais e estrangeiros com o objectivo de &amp;quot;repensar a pr&amp;aacute;tica antropof&amp;aacute;gica na era dos computadores e dos novos media atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma antropofagia das pr&amp;aacute;ticas de media t&amp;aacute;cticos actuais&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote23sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote23anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;23&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. O termo deriva de uma tentativa de adapta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o para o contexto dos media digitais &amp;agrave;s pr&amp;aacute;ticas do movimento art&amp;iacute;stico modernista antrop&amp;oacute;fago surgido nos anos 20 do s&amp;eacute;culo passado que, por sua vez, retomou o conceito de antropofagia, isto &amp;eacute;, as pr&amp;aacute;ticas de canibalismo dos &amp;iacute;ndios brasileiros. &amp;quot;S&amp;oacute; me interessa o que n&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; meu&amp;quot; exclamou o escritor Oswald de Andrade no manifesto fundador do movimento em 1928&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote24sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote24anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;24&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Apesar das ideias de apropria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, justaposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e colagem parecerem estabelecer uma liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com o dada, o surrrealismo e outros movimentos modernistas (Garcia, 2004a), a especificidade do contexto p&amp;oacute;s-colonial do Antropofagismo brasileiro adv&amp;eacute;m desse movimento n&amp;atilde;o tanto de apropria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o mas de absor&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pr&amp;oacute;prio do canibalismo, nas palavras de Garcia (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). Referimo-nos ao ritual da cultura guerreira dos &amp;iacute;ndios Tupi de comer &amp;oacute;rg&amp;atilde;os dos corpos dos seus inimigos ap&amp;oacute;s as batalhas. Ao contr&amp;aacute;rio da vis&amp;atilde;o europeia do canibalismo como uma pr&amp;aacute;tica &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;tabu&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; que classifica o outro de b&amp;aacute;rbaro, ignorante e incivilizado, sendo constitu&amp;iacute;do atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma alteridade radical e amea&amp;ccedil;adora, a cultura ind&amp;iacute;gena estabelece uma assimila&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o rejubilante do outro sem discrimina&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote25sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote25anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;25&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Ao mesmo tempo que comiam os guerreiros mais destemidos das outras tribos para  assimilar a sua for&amp;ccedil;a e coragem, os &amp;iacute;ndios tamb&amp;eacute;m devoravam os colonizadores - que detestavam - de modo a elimin&amp;aacute;-los. O movimento antropof&amp;aacute;gico retoma a ideia de &amp;quot;comer&amp;quot; o que vem do exterior, como as vanguardas europeias da &amp;eacute;poca - e &amp;quot;digeri-lo&amp;quot; misturando-o com as circunst&amp;acirc;ncias locais para criar um novo estilo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote26sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote26anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;26&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Para al&amp;eacute;m dos objectivos concretos do evento Digitofagia tal como est&amp;atilde;o indicados no seu site, o colectivo M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica pode assim ser entendido como um esfor&amp;ccedil;o no sentido de n&amp;atilde;o s&amp;oacute; adaptar o conceito de antropofagia a uma &amp;eacute;poca dominada pela tecnologia digital mas tamb&amp;eacute;m de assimilar as pr&amp;aacute;ticas t&amp;aacute;cticas comuns na Europa Ocidental e na Am&amp;eacute;rica do Norte ao ambiente local. Certo elementos do Met&amp;aacute;fora/Metareciclagem, como Hernani Dimantas, por exemplo, tamb&amp;eacute;m fazem quest&amp;atilde;o em assinalar a liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre esta tradi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o antropof&amp;aacute;gica e a cultura e &amp;eacute;tica &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;hacker&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de fundir elementos de diferentes origens em produtos criativos (Dimantas, 2005; Fonseca, 2003d e 2005).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Foi com a inten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de fomentar novas redes de colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o no campo da inclus&amp;atilde;o digital que os elementos do M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica  criaram em 2005 o IP:// Interface P&amp;uacute;blica&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote27sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote27anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;27&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, que Tatiana Wells descreve como sendo um espa&amp;ccedil;o de trabalho intersectando as &amp;aacute;reas da arte, media, comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e tecnologia. Para al&amp;eacute;m de ser um centro de media no Rio de Janeiro dedicado &amp;agrave; produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o aut&amp;oacute;noma em novos media, &amp;agrave; reciclagem tecnol&amp;oacute;gica - contando mais uma vez com o apoio do Metareciclagem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote28sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote28anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;28&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre, assim como na investiga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma pedagogia cr&amp;iacute;tica dos media. Resultado de uma parceria com o centro de media Sarai, de Nova Deli, e a Sociedade Waag Para os Velho e Novos Media, em Amesterd&amp;atilde;o, do seu programa constam ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e eventos como &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, resid&amp;ecirc;ncias de artistas, activistas e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;hackers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, uma confer&amp;ecirc;ncia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote29sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote29anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;29&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e o alojamento de seis projectos.  Est&amp;aacute; ainda previsto a edi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma publica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. O MetaReciclagem tamb&amp;eacute;m faz parte desta parceria&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote30sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote30anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;30&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.2 - Contratv&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Um dos projectos alojados no IP:// &amp;eacute; a Contratv&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote31sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote31anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;31&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, um colectivo de produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e distribui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de programas televisivos e outras experi&amp;ecirc;ncias narrativas para a Web que v&amp;atilde;o contra o modelo das televis&amp;otilde;es comerciais como a Globo, como por exemplo, &amp;quot;anti-novelas&amp;quot; que alteram o sentido e revelam as mensagens escondidas nas telenovelas, reapropriando-se delas. Este grupo j&amp;aacute; participou em iniciativas anteriores do M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica, tendo sido o respons&amp;aacute;vel pela forma&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o em narrativas digitais nos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; realizados nos Autolabs em colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com o Colectivo de Hist&amp;oacute;rias Digitais e o Museu da Pessoa. No seu site pode-se aceder ao programa desses cursos, &amp;agrave;s p&amp;aacute;ginas concebidas pelos jovens das comunidades abrangidas e aos v&amp;iacute;deos produzidos colectivamente. Quem quiser pode ainda enviar textos, imagens e v&amp;iacute;deos amadores para serem colocados &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. e um guia passo-a-passo explica como &amp;quot;libertar o seu computador&amp;quot;, isto &amp;eacute;, a instalar Linux em computadores Apple baseados no sistema operativo propriet&amp;aacute;rio Mac OS X. Partindo do conceito de &amp;quot;imaginofagia&amp;quot; como resposta &amp;agrave; constru&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e reconstru&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o quotidiana das identidades dos telespectadores exercida pelas esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de televis&amp;atilde;o, a Contratv prop&amp;otilde;e que estes &amp;uacute;ltimos criem os seus pr&amp;oacute;prios programas, reconstruindo assim essa mesma surrealidade de forma a impedir a reprodu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do poder estabelecido. Para tal, disponibiliza &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; um tutorial para a cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de programas Contratv baseados em cinco princ&amp;iacute;pios: amadorismo, n&amp;atilde;o-edi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o - cenas com maior dura&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o -; lentid&amp;atilde;o - de forma a gerar uma monotonia e desprender a aten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do espectador do ecr&amp;atilde; -; subtileza e verosimilhan&amp;ccedil;a - &amp;quot;de modo a mostrar o que a TV n&amp;atilde;o mostra: o dia a dia&amp;quot; (Contratv, s/d).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.3 - Re:combo&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Aplicando ainda mais &amp;agrave; letra do que a Contratv o lema antropof&amp;aacute;gico de &amp;quot;s&amp;oacute; se interessar por tudo aquilo que n&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; seu&amp;quot;, o colectivo Re:combo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote32sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote32anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;32&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; constitui um projecto audiovisual colaborativo baseado nas pr&amp;aacute;ticas da recombina&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, a improvisa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e a intertextualidade que permite efectuar a partir do seu site o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;download&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de m&amp;uacute;sicas e imagens, remistur&amp;aacute;-las e descarregar as novas vers&amp;otilde;es. O grupo &amp;eacute; formado por cerca de 40 elementos, entre m&amp;uacute;sicos, artistas pl&amp;aacute;sticos, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;designers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, programadores, DJs e profissionais de v&amp;iacute;deo. Estes colaboram em v&amp;aacute;rias obras divididos em &amp;quot;c&amp;eacute;lulas de &amp;aacute;udio e v&amp;iacute;deo&amp;quot; espalhadas por cidades do Brasil como Recife, Jo&amp;atilde;o Pessoa, S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, Caruaru e Belo Horizonte que, &amp;agrave; dist&amp;acirc;ncia, via Internet, se dedicam &amp;agrave; produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de novas cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es ou retomando trabalhos em desenvolvimento. Organizam ainda exposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;performances&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; em que colaboram em tempo real com outros DJs da Alemanha, Estados Unidos, Inglaterra e Rom&amp;eacute;nia. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Considerando que o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;copyright&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; representa uma for&amp;ccedil;a restritiva ao processo de cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o art&amp;iacute;stica, inicialmente&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; o Re:combo come&amp;ccedil;ou por remisturar ou samplar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote33sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote33anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;33&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; todos os trabalhos produzidos pelos seus membros ou cujos autores permitiram declaradamente a sua reutiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, explica h.d. mabuse, membro fundador do colectivo em entrevista (Beguelman, 2002). Mas em 2003, introduziu uma licen&amp;ccedil;a de Uso Completo Re:combo (LUCR) para disponibilizar as suas cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e facilitar a reutiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dessas obras por outras pessoas, sem receio de problemas legais. No ano seguinte, a LUCR passou a ser uma licen&amp;ccedil;a Creative Commons aplic&amp;aacute;vel ao &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;sampling&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; ou recombina&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de obras (Re:combo, 2004).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.4 - R&amp;aacute;dios Livres: R&amp;aacute;dio Muda &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.42cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;O movimento das r&amp;aacute;dios livres tem tamb&amp;eacute;m uma grande for&amp;ccedil;a no Brasil e revela bem quer o esp&amp;iacute;rito de colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o existente nesse pa&amp;iacute;s, como tamb&amp;eacute;m a rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o complexa e paradoxal entre os media t&amp;aacute;cticos brasileiros e o governo do PT.  Estas esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es encontram-se reunidas no radiolivre.org&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote34sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote34anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;34&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, um &amp;quot;rizoma&amp;quot; que se destina n&amp;atilde;o s&amp;oacute; &amp;agrave; troca de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, experi&amp;ecirc;ncias e solidariedade, funcionando ainda como um fornecedor de servi&amp;ccedil;os para r&amp;aacute;dios livres, como a transmiss&amp;atilde;o em directo pela Internet, o alojamento de sites, listas de discuss&amp;atilde;o e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;email&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, e o armazenamento de arquivos e f&amp;oacute;runs. Segundo a sec&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de Perguntas e Respostas do seu site, uma r&amp;aacute;dio livre pode ser considerada &amp;quot;uma emissora de baixa pot&amp;ecirc;ncia onde qualquer pessoa pode assumir o papel de programador, locutor ou DJ. A r&amp;aacute;dio procura trocar o conceito de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;broadcasting&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; - de um para muitos - pelo de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;multicasting&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; - de muitos para muitos -, onde todo o cidad&amp;atilde;o e cidad&amp;atilde; pode tanto ouvir r&amp;aacute;dio como participar activamente da constru&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma emissora&amp;quot; (Radiolivre.org, 2005). Distingue-se assim de uma r&amp;aacute;dio comunit&amp;aacute;ria na medida em que nesta &amp;uacute;ltima &amp;eacute; habitualmente &amp;quot;uma associa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que assume para si o dever de informar, manter a programa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e gerir uma emissora&amp;quot;. As primeiras r&amp;aacute;dios livres surgiram no Brasil no in&amp;iacute;cio dos anos 80 e apesar de ainda hoje serem &amp;quot;consideradas ilegais pelo Estado e perseguidas pelas empresas de r&amp;aacute;dio comercial do pa&amp;iacute;s, atrav&amp;eacute;s da Ag&amp;ecirc;ncia Nacional de Telecomunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es (Anatel) e pela Pol&amp;iacute;cia Federal&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote35sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote35anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;35&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, desenvolveram-se bastante nos &amp;uacute;ltimos anos, tendo passado de 100 em 1982 para 1500 em 1995 e 10000 em 2002 (Andriotti, 2004: 110). Tendo em conta a distin&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de Andriotti (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;: 197) e seguindo a dicotomia estabelecida por Garcia e Lovink (1997) e Meikle (2002), poder&amp;iacute;amos assim considerar as r&amp;aacute;dios livres como projectos t&amp;aacute;cticos, na medida em que s&amp;atilde;o emissoras flex&amp;iacute;veis, com uma estrutura aberta, baseadas num modelo de desobedi&amp;ecirc;ncia civil e, por isso mesmo, permanentemente suscept&amp;iacute;veis de serem encerradas pelas autoridades, e as r&amp;aacute;dios comunit&amp;aacute;rias como projectos de media alternativos ou estrat&amp;eacute;gicos, uma vez que apresentam uma estrutura mais centralizada e ligada a movimentos sociais ou pol&amp;iacute;ticos e uma programa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o mais orientada por crit&amp;eacute;rios de qualidade do que pela possibilidade de participa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de todos, uma vez que optaram por institucionalizar-se e seguirem os tr&amp;acirc;mites da lei, de modo a serem aceites pelo Estado. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.42cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.42cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Uma das r&amp;aacute;dios livres que tem sido frequentemente alvo de mandatos de encerramento &amp;eacute; a R&amp;aacute;dio Muda, que surgiu na segunda metade da d&amp;eacute;cada de 80 no seio da Universidade Estadual de Campinas (Unicamp) e que tem o seu est&amp;uacute;dio numa caixa de &amp;aacute;gua na pra&amp;ccedil;a central do campus. A esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o transmite para toda a cidade com uma pot&amp;ecirc;ncia de 50 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;watts&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; na frequ&amp;ecirc;ncia 105.7 MHz e, atrav&amp;eacute;s de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;streaming&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; pela Internet, para todo o mundo. O seu nome deve-se &amp;agrave;s in&amp;uacute;meras suspens&amp;otilde;es e paragens derivado a problemas legais e t&amp;eacute;cnicos, que continuam ainda hoje, mesmo ap&amp;oacute;s o novo governo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote36sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote36anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;36&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Como menciona Andriotti (2004: 151), a sua hist&amp;oacute;ria est&amp;aacute; associada &amp;agrave; hist&amp;oacute;ria de resist&amp;ecirc;ncia e livre apropria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do meio r&amp;aacute;dio, sendo vista como &amp;quot;uma refer&amp;ecirc;ncia nacional de r&amp;aacute;dio popular e democr&amp;aacute;tica&amp;quot;. Esta emissora esteve sempre ligada &amp;agrave; quest&amp;atilde;o da liberta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de frequ&amp;ecirc;ncias radiof&amp;oacute;nicas para apropria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o p&amp;uacute;blica. H&amp;aacute;  mais de dez anos que se desvinculou da associa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de estudantes local,  funcionando desde ent&amp;atilde;o como uma iniciativa aut&amp;oacute;noma, possuindo uma estrutura de organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o horizontal, em que o colectivo respons&amp;aacute;vel pela sua gest&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; composto pelos pr&amp;oacute;prios programadores - que rondam os 200, para um total de cerca de 100 programas inscritos (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;: 162) e a emiss&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; aberta a todo o p&amp;uacute;blico, na medida em que qualquer pessoa pode difundir o seu programa. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 1cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;A R&amp;aacute;dio Muda tem estabelecido v&amp;aacute;rias parcerias com outros colectivos de media t&amp;aacute;cticos e alternativos. Para al&amp;eacute;m da parceria com o M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica, atrav&amp;eacute;s dos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; ministrados no &amp;acirc;mbito dos Autolabs com o atrav&amp;eacute;s de um subgrupo de programadores, a Submidia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote37sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote37anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;37&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, esta esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o mant&amp;eacute;m uma colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o regular com o Centro de Media Independente do Brasil. A transmiss&amp;atilde;o da  r&amp;aacute;dio pela Internet &amp;eacute; possibilitada mediante o alojamento da emiss&amp;atilde;o num servidor do CMI em Inglaterra, atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma tecnologia de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre. Esta alian&amp;ccedil;a - a que n&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; alheia a exist&amp;ecirc;ncia de v&amp;aacute;rias afinidades entre os dois colectivos, no sentido em que ambos assumem uma estrutura descentralizada e rejeitarem a intermedia&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do mercado nos media - estabeleceu-se na segunda edi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do F&amp;oacute;rum Social Mundial&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote38sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote38anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;38&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, em Janeiro de 2002, na cidade de Porto Alegre, onde o CMI possu&amp;iacute;a um ponto de acesso &amp;agrave; Internet e uma equipa de t&amp;eacute;cnicos especializados (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;ibidem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;: 204): &amp;quot;Ali mesmo no Acampamento da Juventude durante o II F&amp;oacute;rum Social Mundial &amp;eacute; realizada com sucesso a primeira experi&amp;ecirc;ncia de transmiss&amp;atilde;o do sinal da R&amp;aacute;dio Muda via Internet.&amp;quot; A partir desse encontro, surgiu a ideia de criar uma rede de r&amp;aacute;dios livres brasileiras que se concretizou com o desenvolvimento do site radiolivre.org. O projecto tem tamb&amp;eacute;m o objectivo adicional de permitir a retransmiss&amp;atilde;o de toda a programa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o das r&amp;aacute;dios livres pela Internet (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;ibidem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;: 211). Outra colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com o CMI foi a cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da r&amp;aacute;dio livre &amp;quot;Pega Eu&amp;quot; que funcionou durante o per&amp;iacute;odo de dura&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do Festival Midia T&amp;aacute;tica em Mar&amp;ccedil;o de 2003, em directo da Casa das Rosas &amp;quot;com os microfones abertos a qualquer um que deles se quisesse apropriar, al&amp;eacute;m das tradicionais oficinas&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;ibidem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, 223). O CMI elaborou uma carta que foi enviada &amp;agrave; Anatel e ao governo federal uma semana antes do evento em que anunciava a cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e desafiava as autoridades a virem fechar a r&amp;aacute;dio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote39sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote39anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;39&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;.  Este acto de desobedi&amp;ecirc;ncia civil serviu para gerar uma maior visibilidade para a quest&amp;atilde;o dos encerramentos das emissoras livres, aproveitando a presen&amp;ccedil;a dos media comerciais no local. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.5 - CMI-Brasil&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Pelo que pudemos ver at&amp;eacute; agora, o CMI-Brasil t&amp;ecirc;m desempenhado um papel fundamental na coordena&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de iniciativas activistas de car&amp;aacute;cter t&amp;aacute;ctico no pa&amp;iacute;s. Apesar de j&amp;aacute; termos abordado a rede Indymedia e o CMI-Portugal, achamos que seria importante mencionar aqui as actividades deste Centro de Media Independente que se destacam e se distinguem de outros CMIs. Actualmente, conta com 11 centros em grandes cidades brasileiras, encontrando-se em processo de forma&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o mais 13 outros n&amp;uacute;cleos espalhados pelo Brasil&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote40sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote40anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;40&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Tendo surgido em Setembro de 2000, no seguimento de protestos do movimento por uma globaliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o alternativa contra a reuni&amp;atilde;o do FMI e do Banco Mundial que decorreu nesse m&amp;ecirc;s em Praga, o CMI-Brasil colocou o seu site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; em Dezembro de 2000 (Cabral, 2005). Devido &amp;agrave; disparidade de acesso &amp;agrave; Internet e &amp;agrave;s tecnologias digitais existente no pa&amp;iacute;s, os colectivos locais procuraram &amp;ldquo;combinar a tecnologia digital e de internet com os meios tradicionais de forma a potencializ&amp;aacute;-los&amp;quot;, explica Pablo Ortellado, do Indymedia brasileiro (Ortellado, 2003).  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;No campo da r&amp;aacute;dio, por exemplo, para al&amp;eacute;m da colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com a R&amp;aacute;dio Muda, o CMI-Brasil integrou o projecto da &amp;Aacute;rea de R&amp;aacute;dios Livres das Am&amp;eacute;ricas (ARLA) em paralelo com o Encontro de R&amp;aacute;dios Livres em Novembro de 2003, permitindo a cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma emiss&amp;atilde;o radiof&amp;oacute;nica conjunta transmitida pela Web&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote41sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote41anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;41&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; destinada a realizar a cobertura das mobiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es contra a &amp;Aacute;rea de Livre-Com&amp;eacute;rcio das Am&amp;eacute;ricas (ALCA), durante a reuni&amp;atilde;o em Miami dos respons&amp;aacute;veis por este organismo regional impulsionado pelos Estados Unidos. Outra ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do CMI-Brasil que resulta da colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com as r&amp;aacute;dios locais &amp;eacute; a produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de um boletim de not&amp;iacute;cias seleccionados do seu site que &amp;eacute; enviado para r&amp;aacute;dios livres e comunit&amp;aacute;rias que, entre outras, abrange dezenas de esta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es localizadas na regi&amp;atilde;o de Porto Alegre. Isso permite estabelecer um interc&amp;acirc;mbio m&amp;uacute;tuo, j&amp;aacute; que as r&amp;aacute;dios tamb&amp;eacute;m enviam not&amp;iacute;cias das suas comunidades locais para os colectivos Indymedia no Brasil, nota Ortellado (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Um dos media com que os colectivos brasileiros da Indymedia t&amp;ecirc;m obtido mais visibilidade &amp;eacute; o v&amp;iacute;deo. O document&amp;aacute;rio &amp;quot;N&amp;atilde;o come&amp;ccedil;ou em Seattle, n&amp;atilde;o vai terminar em Quebec (A20)&amp;quot;, realizado pelo n&amp;uacute;cleo do Rio de Janeiro que filmou as manifesta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es contra a ALCA em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, no m&amp;ecirc;s  de Abril de 2001&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote42sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote42anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;42&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;.  Tendo em conta as dificuldades financeiras e de acesso &amp;agrave; Rede da popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, o CMI nacional possibilita n&amp;atilde;o s&amp;oacute; a publica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de v&amp;iacute;deos no seu site, tal como o centro portugu&amp;ecirc;s, mas conjuga esfor&amp;ccedil;os com outros grupos activistas de v&amp;iacute;deo e associa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es locais para a facilita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de espa&amp;ccedil;os de exibi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. A coopera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o internacional atrav&amp;eacute;s da Internet facilita a troca e difus&amp;atilde;o de v&amp;iacute;deos com centros de outros pa&amp;iacute;ses. Ortellado salienta que esta rede de distribui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o permitiu que o document&amp;aacute;rio sobre os protestos contra a ALCA &amp;quot;fossem vistos por mais de 20 mil pessoas ou que comunidades de sem-abrigo em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo ou de favelas no Rio de Janeiro conhecessem uma realidade semelhante, a dos trabalhadores desempregados de Buenos Aires&amp;quot;  (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;ibidem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Tal como o colectivo portugu&amp;ecirc;s, os n&amp;uacute;cleos do CMI-Brasil produzem &amp;quot;jornais relativamente peri&amp;oacute;dicos, com pequena tiragem, como o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;A&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o Direta&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo que s&amp;atilde;o distribu&amp;iacute;dos para organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sociais diversas, em determinadas localidades ou eventos&amp;quot; (Cabral, 2005). Devido &amp;agrave; falta de recursos e de t&amp;eacute;cnicos especializados, os volunt&amp;aacute;rios brasileiros optaram por passar a produzir jornais-murais, em tamanho A3 com uma periodicidade mais ou menos regular, afixados em muros, paredes e paragens de autocarro de cidades como Rio de Janeiro, Fortaleza e Florian&amp;oacute;polis. Ortellado considera que esta solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o permite aumentar o n&amp;uacute;mero de leitores com um custo muito baixo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;O CMI-Brasil actua ainda ao n&amp;iacute;vel da inclus&amp;atilde;o digital atrav&amp;eacute;s da constitui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de centros de acesso p&amp;uacute;blico &amp;agrave; Internet com computadores equipados com &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; livre, semelhantes aos Autolabs e aos Telecentros. Em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, o colectivo local instalou um cibercaf&amp;eacute; numa ocupa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o urbana - &amp;quot;actualmente  funciona em conjunto com a ONG A&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o Educativa - que resultou na cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma r&amp;aacute;dio livre com transmiss&amp;atilde;o via Internet montada por crian&amp;ccedil;as de oito a 12 anos, ap&amp;oacute;s a participa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o num curso ministrado no local (Ortellado, 2003; Cabral, 2005). Mas de acordo com Ortellado, o objectivo &amp;eacute; abrir mais cibercaf&amp;eacute;s CMI noutras cidades. De forma a adaptar o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; livre para  produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o medi&amp;aacute;tica j&amp;aacute; existente para portugu&amp;ecirc;s, est&amp;aacute; a ser desenvolvida uma distribui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de Linux espec&amp;iacute;fica chamada Indymix que dever&amp;aacute; ser implementada nos futuros centros de acesso p&amp;uacute;blico. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Adaptando o conceito dos cibercaf&amp;eacute;s CMI para um cen&amp;aacute;rio &amp;quot;no terreno&amp;quot;, os colectivos t&amp;ecirc;m vindo a desenvolver laborat&amp;oacute;rios tempor&amp;aacute;rios de media em eventos especiais. Estes espa&amp;ccedil;os ministram um conjunto de cursos integrados e colectivos dos quais resulta uma produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o constante e cont&amp;iacute;nua de conte&amp;uacute;dos de media com participa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o livre e aberta a todos. As primeira experi&amp;ecirc;ncias do CMI-Brasil com laborat&amp;oacute;rios de media decorreram durante a terceira edi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do F&amp;oacute;rum Social Mundial de Porto Alegre, em Jameiro de 2003 e durante o Primeiro F&amp;oacute;rum Social Brasileiro, que teve lugar em Belo Horizonte no m&amp;ecirc;s de Novembro desse mesmo ano. No &amp;uacute;ltimo caso, tratou-se da Casa Macuna&amp;iacute;ma, um local onde v&amp;aacute;rios comunicadores e jornalistas que estavam a fazer a cobertura do F&amp;oacute;rum se puderam congregar e colaborar na produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de pe&amp;ccedil;as audiovisuais, representando &amp;quot;um espa&amp;ccedil;o colectivo de comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o democr&amp;aacute;tica&amp;quot; (Cabral, 2005) que contou com o apoio da Associa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o Brasileira de Radiodifus&amp;atilde;o Comunit&amp;aacute;ria (ABRACO) - &amp;oacute;rg&amp;atilde;o representante das r&amp;aacute;dios comunit&amp;aacute;rias brasileiras. O &amp;ecirc;xito da iniciativa levou &amp;agrave; cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de um novo espa&amp;ccedil;o Macuna&amp;iacute;ma durante o F&amp;oacute;rum Mundial da Educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que decorreu em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo em Abril de 2004. Posteriormente, foi ainda implementado um outro laborat&amp;oacute;rio de media, o Polim&amp;iacute;dia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote43sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote43anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;43&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;, que integrou a programa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o oficial da 4&amp;ordf; Confer&amp;ecirc;ncia da Rede OurMedia, dedicada ao estudo e investiga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos media alternativos e independentes, realizada em Julho de 2004 novamente em Porto Alegre. Nesse espa&amp;ccedil;o, activistas do CMI, produtores independente e investigadores acad&amp;eacute;micos puderam efectuar colaborativamente experi&amp;ecirc;ncias pr&amp;aacute;ticas de comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e desenvolvimento e trocar conhecimentos, atrav&amp;eacute;s de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; e apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de projecto relacionados com a utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o aut&amp;oacute;noma e comunit&amp;aacute;ria do v&amp;iacute;deo, da r&amp;aacute;dio e da Internet (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;1.6 &amp;ndash; Brasil, Na&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hacker&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;O que resulta da an&amp;aacute;lise do trabalho de todos os projectos aqui referenciados &amp;eacute; uma tentativa de transposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o daquilo a que poder&amp;iacute;amos chamar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;jeitinho&amp;quot; brasileiro para o dom&amp;iacute;nio dos media e das tecnologias digitais. Esta express&amp;atilde;o popular pode ser definida como uma &amp;quot;maneira h&amp;aacute;bil, esperta, astuciosa de conseguir alguma coisa, especialmente algo que &amp;agrave; maioria das pessoas se afigura particularmente dif&amp;iacute;cil&amp;quot;, recorrendo &amp;agrave; economia informal ou mesmo marginal. A &amp;quot;gambiarra&amp;quot; ou &amp;quot;gato&amp;quot; &amp;eacute; um dos exemplos desse &amp;quot;jeitinho&amp;quot; aplicado na pr&amp;aacute;tica que os elementos do Midia T&amp;aacute;tica referem no site do Digitofagia e que se insere na cultura antropof&amp;aacute;gica de apropria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o daquilo que &amp;eacute; do outro. Trata-se de &amp;quot;uma extens&amp;atilde;o puxada fraudulentamente para furtar energia el&amp;eacute;ctrica&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote44sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote44anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;44&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; geralmente utilizada em favelas ou ocupa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de casas e terras.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;A &amp;quot;gambiarra&amp;quot;, tanto em sentido literal ou como met&amp;aacute;fora para a subvers&amp;atilde;o da tecnologia e dos media - como se se tratasse de um &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;hack&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; -, na nova interpreta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que o colectivo M&amp;iacute;dia T&amp;aacute;tica faz da palavra, apresenta-se assim como um dos exemplos mais concretos e realistas das ast&amp;uacute;cias t&amp;aacute;cticas que Michel de Certeau assinalou, uma vez que elas s&amp;atilde;o incorporadas pelas popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es no seu quotidiano. Em &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;Arts de Faire&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;, o autor franc&amp;ecirc;s chega mesmo a fazer v&amp;aacute;rias refer&amp;ecirc;ncias ao modo como a cultura popular brasileira resiste &amp;agrave; assimila&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pelo outro, um poder externo, recorrendo a linguagens e cren&amp;ccedil;as populares pr&amp;oacute;prias para subverter a l&amp;iacute;ngua imposta pelo colonizador e a religi&amp;atilde;o imposta pelo mission&amp;aacute;rio, chamando a  esse tipo de sabedoria um misto de estratagema - trampolinagem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote45sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote45anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;45&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; - e de trapa&amp;ccedil;aria, isto &amp;eacute;, ast&amp;uacute;cia e esperteza no modo de utilizar ou de esquivar-se aos termos do contrato social (Certeau, 1990 [1980]: 34). Mas estas &amp;quot;mil maneiras de jogar/desfazer o jogo do outro&amp;quot; representam, na nossa opini&amp;atilde;o, mais que &amp;quot;um prazer em alterar as regras do espa&amp;ccedil;o opressor&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;). Apesar da alegria e o gozo estarem habitualmente presentes, o que est&amp;aacute; em quest&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; quase sempre a sobreviv&amp;ecirc;ncia no dia a dia. O mesmo se passa com as novas &amp;quot;gambiarras&amp;quot; digitais. Dados os enormes problemas que a popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o brasileira tem que enfrentar, a resposta n&amp;atilde;o reside num mero pessimismo mas num &amp;quot;talento intermin&amp;aacute;vel para a improvisa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, para vislumbrar (e criar) possibilidades&amp;quot;, tal como salienta David Garcia que inventou a apropriada designa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de &amp;quot;terra do possibilismo&amp;quot; para descrever o ambiente que, &amp;quot;contra todas as probabilidades&amp;quot;, encontrou no Brasil (Garcia, 2004a). Assim n&amp;atilde;o podemos ver estas pr&amp;aacute;ticas &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;Do-It-Yourself&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; que identific&amp;aacute;mos neste cap&amp;iacute;tulo como meros media t&amp;aacute;cticos mas &amp;quot;como um m&amp;eacute;todo pr&amp;aacute;tico de fazer coisas para alterar os sistemas, de n&amp;atilde;o esperar para que o governo ou as institui&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es fa&amp;ccedil;am o trabalho&amp;quot;, nas palavras de Brunet (2005). Falando como brasileira, esta autora faz quest&amp;atilde;o de salientar que &amp;quot;no Brasil, n&amp;oacute;s temos que lutar para obter estas coisas (alimenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e sa&amp;uacute;de). N&amp;atilde;o sobrevivemos se esperarmos pelo governo. &amp;Eacute; por isso que aqui surgem muitos estilos de vida alternativos&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;). Essa luta pela sobreviv&amp;ecirc;ncia face aos graves problemas econ&amp;oacute;micos do pa&amp;iacute;s e &amp;agrave; dificuldade em arranjar emprego na economia formal t&amp;ecirc;m levado milh&amp;otilde;es de brasileiros a recorrerem a esquemas mais ou menos il&amp;iacute;citos no dom&amp;iacute;nio da economia informal. Em 2004, 60 por cento da popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o activa, isto &amp;eacute;, 47,5 milh&amp;otilde;es de pessoas, estavam na informalidade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote46sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote46anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;46&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;. Felipe Fonseca chama a esse &amp;quot;mundo alternativo de trabalho&amp;quot; de &amp;quot;economia pirata&amp;quot;, caracterizada pela criatividade e pelo dinamismo, um &amp;quot;empreendedorismo&amp;quot; na gambiarra, tendo um c&amp;iacute;rculo pr&amp;oacute;prio de produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e distribui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o (Fonseca, 2005). Uma das suas figuras &amp;eacute; o &amp;quot;camel&amp;ocirc;&amp;quot;, o vendedor ambulante ou instalado num local fixo que, por conta pr&amp;oacute;pria e frequentemente desafiando a lei - escapando ao pagamento de impostos -, comercializa produtos contrabandeados e at&amp;eacute; falsificados em barracas ou bancas pelas pra&amp;ccedil;as e ruas das cidades do pa&amp;iacute;s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote47sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote47anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;47&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;. Felipe Fonseca descobre um elo de liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre o camel&amp;ocirc; e os &amp;quot;media t&amp;aacute;cticos do primeiro mundo, na medida em que ao optar pela venda de CDs, DVDs e jogos pirateados para obter a sua subsist&amp;ecirc;ncia, aquele &amp;quot;tamb&amp;eacute;m chega (...) a questionar os dom&amp;iacute;nios da propriedade intelectual e do poder dos media de massas, em especial, o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;branding&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; empresarial&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote48sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote48anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;48&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Mas da mesma forma que o &amp;quot;jeitinho&amp;quot; brasileiro &amp;eacute; simbolizado pelas &amp;quot;gambiarras&amp;quot;, as ast&amp;uacute;cias e manhas dos fracos para fugir aos espa&amp;ccedil;os e muros erguidos pelos outros, tamb&amp;eacute;m o &amp;eacute; pela colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, pela generosidade e pela cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de solidariedades entre identidades distintas mas que partilham a sua condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de exclu&amp;iacute;dos, tendo por isso um interesse comum: sobreviver no quotidiano. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Os activistas t&amp;aacute;cticos brasileiros possuem uma consci&amp;ecirc;ncia profunda de que no Brasil &amp;quot;a periferia &amp;eacute; o centro&amp;quot; (Dimantas, 2004 e 2005; Estraviz, 2001), na medida em que &amp;quot;l&amp;aacute; a comunidade se organiza&amp;quot; (Estraviz, 2001) e colabora colectivamente&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote49sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote49anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;49&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Do mesmo modo que as &amp;quot;gambiarras&amp;quot; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;DIY&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, &amp;quot;a colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o aqui (no Brasil) &amp;eacute; sempre uma estrat&amp;eacute;gia de sobreviv&amp;ecirc;ncia&amp;quot;, afirma Hernani Dimantas, que acrescenta: &amp;quot;O que seria deste pa&amp;iacute;s se n&amp;atilde;o fosse a gentileza entre pessoas que jogam na mesma equipa da mis&amp;eacute;ria, os agora chamados &#039;exclu&amp;iacute;dos&#039;&amp;quot; (Dimantas, 2005). Essa ideia fica bem expressa na cultura popular brasileira atrav&amp;eacute;s do conceito de &amp;quot;mutir&amp;atilde;o&amp;quot;, que pode ser definido como &amp;quot;qualquer mobiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o colectiva e gratuita de cidad&amp;atilde;os para execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de um servi&amp;ccedil;o que beneficie a comunidade&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote50sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote50anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;50&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Este termo &amp;eacute; frequentemente utilizado pelos membros do Met&amp;aacute;fora e do Metareciclagem para descreverem as suas ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es com a tecnologia digital e a sociedade brasileira. Para Dimantas, por exemplo, a periferia &amp;eacute; o centro&amp;quot; porque &amp;quot;vive de mutir&amp;atilde;o, respira colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). Um mutir&amp;atilde;o tanto pode ser uma ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o conjunta de limpeza das ruas de um bairro, a pintura de uma creche ou uma escola de samba. O &amp;quot;puxadinho&amp;quot; ou &amp;quot;puxada&amp;quot; &amp;eacute;, no entanto, talvez o exemplo mais pertinente do que um &amp;quot;mutir&amp;atilde;o&amp;quot; pode ser na pr&amp;aacute;tica, referindo-se ao costume de &amp;quot;acrescentar uma ou duas divis&amp;otilde;es de uma casa, aproveitando uma das paredes externas&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote51sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote51anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;51&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; quando uma fam&amp;iacute;lia se torna mais numerosa atrav&amp;eacute;s do casamento de um filho ou do nascimento de mais outro. Esta &amp;eacute; assim, tal como a &amp;quot;gambiarra&amp;quot; uma forma de improvisar e solucionar um problema concreto do quotidiano de milh&amp;otilde;es de brasileiros: a falta de espa&amp;ccedil;o para habita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e de recursos financeiros para comprar uma nova casa. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;A import&amp;acirc;ncia da colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre pessoas repercutiu na tentativa dos activistas brasileiros trabalhando com media t&amp;aacute;cticos de adaptarem este e outros conceitos originalmente criados na Europa e Am&amp;eacute;rica do Norte para o contexto brasileiro. &amp;quot;Em termos de colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, n&amp;oacute;s, elite cultural revoltadinha brasileira, temos mais a aprender do que a ensinar com as culturas populares&amp;quot;, refere Felipe Fonseca (2005). A proposta destes colectivos pode, efectivamente, ser vista como uma digitofagia, uma antropofagia das tecnologias digitais e dos media anal&amp;oacute;gicos mais acess&amp;iacute;veis que combina tra&amp;ccedil;os comuns da cultura popular brasileira com a &amp;eacute;tica &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;hacker&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;: colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, descentraliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, &amp;ecirc;nfase na reputa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e informalidade (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote52sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote52anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;52&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma nova abordagem da inclus&amp;atilde;o digital que vai para al&amp;eacute;m do mero acesso &amp;agrave;s tecnologias digitais, os projectos atr&amp;aacute;s referidos, assim como o Met&amp;aacute;fora/Metareciclagem, tentam oferecer &amp;agrave; popula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de baixos rendimentos e que vive na periferia meios para ampliar sua voz, para se reapropriar da tecnologia tendo em conta as suas necessidades e os seus interesses. Porque apesar de essas pessoas estarem exclu&amp;iacute;das do acesso &amp;agrave;s ferramentas tecnol&amp;oacute;gicas, elas n&amp;atilde;o est&amp;atilde;o exclu&amp;iacute;das da cultura da colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, da criatividade e da sobreviv&amp;ecirc;ncia (Dimantas, 2005). Elas &amp;ldquo;s&amp;atilde;o capazes de tomar as pr&amp;oacute;prias r&amp;eacute;deas, andar sozinhas e protagonizar suas pr&amp;oacute;prias vidas&amp;rdquo; (Dimantas, 2004). Com vista &amp;agrave; reapropria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da tecnologia pela sociedade brasileira, Felipe Fonseca sugere que em vez de tentarem transformar um &amp;quot;camel&amp;ocirc;&amp;quot; num funcion&amp;aacute;rio de escrit&amp;oacute;rio, os coordenadores de projectos p&amp;uacute;blicos e do terceiro sector de inclus&amp;atilde;o digital deviam pensar como &amp;eacute; que a tecnologia pode melhorar a sua actividade de venda em locais p&amp;uacute;blico (Fonseca, 2005a). Fonseca prop&amp;otilde;e ainda que se aproveite as caracter&amp;iacute;sticas culturais brasileiras para obter o m&amp;aacute;ximo das tecnologias fomentando o recurso &amp;agrave; Internet por essas pessoas da periferia onde se estabele&amp;ccedil;a &amp;quot;a troca de conhecimentos, a colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e a mobiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o colectiva&amp;quot; (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). Em lugar de uma &amp;ldquo;inclus&amp;atilde;o digital&amp;rdquo; que entende o computador e a Internet como ferramentas de empregabilidade, projectos como o Met&amp;aacute;fora/Metareciclagem apontam para um caminho alternativo em que a tecnologia facilita a comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o das pessoas da periferia entre si e destas para com a sociedade.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.03cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; page-break-before: always;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;2 &amp;ndash; Projecto Met&amp;aacute;fora: Caos e Ordem numa Intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia Colectiva&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Hoje em dia, a maior dificuldade para come&amp;ccedil;ar um projeto de pesquisa &amp;eacute; a defini&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do nome. Que nome dar a um projecto que tem por objetivo entender e propor aplica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para uma realidade em que passaremos do &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online/offline&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; para uma cultura permanentemente conectada? Como definir uma cultura em que definir o nome de um projecto &amp;eacute; mais dif&amp;iacute;cil do que estabelecer um f&amp;oacute;rum de comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre os seus membros? E isso &amp;eacute; s&amp;oacute; o come&amp;ccedil;o. Virtualiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da presen&amp;ccedil;a, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;k-logs&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote53sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote53anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;53&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;m-log&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote54sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote54anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;54&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;s&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, RSS, telecentros comunit&amp;aacute;rios, intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia colectiva, o novo nomadismo, s&amp;atilde;o alguns dos assuntos que v&amp;atilde;o nos guiar.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;- Felipe Fonseca, &amp;ldquo;Met&amp;aacute;fora&amp;rdquo;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Foi com esta frase em ep&amp;iacute;grafe enviada para uma nova lista de discuss&amp;atilde;o por &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;email&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; que se deu in&amp;iacute;cio ao projecto Met&amp;aacute;fora, a 28 de Junho de 2002&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote55sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote55anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;55&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. O objectivo era trocar ideias e talvez conceber tecnologias que incorporassem na pr&amp;aacute;tica no&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es como conhecimento livre, redes sociais, colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;copyleft&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote56sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote56anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;56&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Na origem do Met&amp;aacute;fora esteve outra lista, a Joelhasso, que tamb&amp;eacute;m servia de nome a um &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;blog&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; criado por Felipe Fonseca em 2001, que trabalhava na altura na ind&amp;uacute;stria da publicidade. A&amp;iacute; se congregaram virtualmente os integrantes de outras listas brasileiras sobre &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;marketing&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, entre os quais Hernani Dimantas, Paulo Bicarato e Charles Pilger, que viriam mais tarde a fazer parte do Met&amp;aacute;fora. Como conta Fonseca, os assuntos em discuss&amp;atilde;o na Joelhasso abrangiam a Internet sem fios, dispositivos em rede, XML, integra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de equipamentos e conversa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es (2005). Desagradados pelo que consideravam ser o atraso da ind&amp;uacute;stria tecnol&amp;oacute;gica brasileira, Fonseca e Dimantas criaram em jeito de resposta a primeira &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;mailing-list&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; Met&amp;aacute;fora com o intuito, nas palavras do primeiro, de &amp;quot;tentar consolidar as novas ideias que um monte de gente estava gerando&amp;quot;. Na entrevista que realiz&amp;aacute;mos, Fonseca esclarece que o Met&amp;aacute;fora surgiu como uma sa&amp;iacute;da para a frustra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que sentia no seu emprego  na altura: &amp;ldquo;O Projecto Met&amp;aacute;fora tornou-se o ambiente onde a criatividade n&amp;atilde;o enontrava limites e onde come&amp;ccedil;avam a aparecer pessoas que tinham interesses e perspectivas em comum comigo&amp;rdquo; (Fonseca, 2005b). Hernani Dimantas complementa essa afirma&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, afirmando que &amp;ldquo;o car&amp;aacute;cter aberto do projecto deu ao grupo as possibilidades para o exerc&amp;iacute;cio total da criatividade&amp;rdquo; (Dimantas, 2004). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tendo em conta um &amp;quot;quotidiano hiperconectado&amp;quot;, a lista visava estimular o debate sobre &amp;quot;os limites cada vez mais t&amp;eacute;nues entre &lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt; e &lt;i&gt;offline&lt;/i&gt;, entre digital e anal&amp;oacute;gico, e o conhecimento livre como metodologia de colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;quot; em que se passasse para al&amp;eacute;m da cr&amp;iacute;tica, no sentido da apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de alternativas concretas (Fonseca, 2005).  No mesmo texto, Fonseca recorda o processo de forma&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da nova comunidade &lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;: &amp;quot;Criei a lista de discuss&amp;atilde;o no Yahoo! Groups e convidei 12 pessoas. Quase todas aceitaram&amp;quot; (&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;).  Dimantas afirma a este prop&amp;oacute;sito que ambos combinaram inicialmente que ele faria a articula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o externa e Fonseca ficaria a cargo da articula&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o interna. &amp;quot;Abri o di&amp;aacute;logo do Meta com institui&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do governo, algumas ONGs mais institucionalizadas e com participa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pol&amp;iacute;tica e a academia&amp;quot;, refere no question&amp;aacute;rio que elabor&amp;aacute;mos. Por seu lado, Fonseca &amp;ndash; que utilizava nesses primeiros tempos a alcunha &lt;i&gt;Izquierdo, El Horrible&lt;/i&gt; - incentivava as pessoas que iam chegando &amp;agrave; lista a conversarem entre si. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;A lista come&amp;ccedil;ou por ser uma conversa entre um grupo de 15 pessoas, mas no per&amp;iacute;odo de um m&amp;ecirc;s j&amp;aacute; tinham sido a&amp;iacute; publicadas mais de 1200 mensagens entre 45 elementos. Foi assim criada uma &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; onde come&amp;ccedil;aram a ser guardados os in&amp;uacute;meros &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;bookmarks&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de not&amp;iacute;cias e artigos que eram debatidos na lista (Fonseca, 2003). De seguida, foi redigido o rascunho de um projecto. Tr&amp;ecirc;s dias mais tarde, este rascunho transformou-se na descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o completa de um projecto, tendo os participantes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt; &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;come&amp;ccedil;ado a elaborar projectos colaborativos a partir da &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;wiki (idem)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. O Met&amp;aacute;fora viria a acabar em Outubro de 2003. Um m&amp;ecirc;s antes, durante a sua interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o no N5M, em Amesterd&amp;atilde;o, Felipe Fonseca afirmava que o Met&amp;aacute;fora contava com &amp;ldquo;cerca de 200 pessoas, desde &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;lurkers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote57sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote57anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;57&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; a gestores de projectos, e mais de 25 projectos, estando actualmente quase metade deles a serem desenvolvidos&amp;rdquo;, todos eles funcionando gra&amp;ccedil;as ao voluntariado dos participantes (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;ibidem&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;). Embora a grande maioria dos elementos mais activos do Met&amp;aacute;fora tenha pertencido &amp;agrave; regi&amp;atilde;o de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo, o projecto alastrou-se tamb&amp;eacute;m a outras cidades brasileiras como Belo Horizonte e Rio de Janeiro, contando ainda com participantes nos Estados Unidos.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;De in&amp;iacute;cio, as conversas na lista, versando sobre telem&amp;oacute;veis ligados &amp;agrave; Internet, &lt;i&gt;m-blogs&lt;/i&gt;, PDAs e computadores de bolso, evidenciavam um certo pendor para o tecno-narcissismo que, como Matteo Pasquinelli acusa (2002), predomina em muitos projectos aut&amp;oacute;nomos trabalhando com media e tecnologia. Gradualmente, no entanto, assistiu-se a um desviar da aten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o sobre a tecnologia em si para uma maior consciencializa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o sobre as necessidades reais das pessoas comuns de forma a ir de encontro a elas&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote58sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote58anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;58&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: -0.02cm; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tal como outros grupos abordados anteriormente, o Met&amp;aacute;fora conseguiu juntar no mesmo projecto &lt;i&gt;hackers&lt;/i&gt;, fil&amp;oacute;sofos, jornalistas, artistas, antrop&amp;oacute;logos e &lt;i&gt;designers&lt;/i&gt;, todos eles actuando em quatro grandes &amp;agrave;reas: comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, tecnologia, educa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e arte. &amp;ldquo;O Met&amp;aacute;fora &amp;eacute; totalmente independente. &amp;Eacute; aberto e flex&amp;iacute;vel. N&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; um projeto acad&amp;eacute;mico. &amp;Eacute; uma nova forma de gerar conhecimento. O nosso enfoque &amp;eacute; o incentivo de projectos pessoais atrav&amp;eacute;s da colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre os participantes&amp;rdquo;, explicou Hernani Dimantas (2004). O car&amp;aacute;cter transdisciplinar do projecto &amp;eacute; recordado por Felipe Fonseca: &amp;ldquo;Baseados em tecnologia que hoje (Novembro de 2005) at&amp;eacute; parece pouco sofisticada (uma &lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt; e uma lista de discuss&amp;atilde;o), fomos capazes de mobilizar efectivamente mais de uma centena de pessoas dispostas a experimentar novas formas de lidar com o conhecimento e de encontrar solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para problemas em comum&amp;rdquo; (Fonseca, 2005b). Esta converg&amp;ecirc;ncia de esfor&amp;ccedil;os resultou naquilo a que o colectivo denominou de aprendizagem distribu&amp;iacute;da em que &amp;ldquo;um grande n&amp;uacute;mero de pessoas com os mais variados repert&amp;oacute;rios, esfor&amp;ccedil;ando-se por fugir aos jarg&amp;otilde;es e por expressar-se de uma maneira que todos compreendessem, foram respons&amp;aacute;veis por uma dissemina&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o multilateral de conhecimento com um ritmo que eu nunca tinha visto&amp;rdquo; (&lt;i&gt;idem&lt;/i&gt;).  Na base desta &amp;ldquo;comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o multi-facetada, multi-lateral, interactiva e independente&amp;rdquo; (Dimantas, 2004) esteve a ideia de &amp;ldquo;xemel&amp;ecirc;&amp;rdquo;, que Fonseca define como sendo &amp;ldquo;um esfor&amp;ccedil;o positivo no sentido de manter um n&amp;iacute;vel de linguagem que pudesse ser mutuamente compreens&amp;iacute;vel&amp;rdquo; de modo a que todos pudessem participar nas discuss&amp;otilde;es (Fonseca, 2005)&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote59sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote59anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;59&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. O termo remete para um epis&amp;oacute;dio concreto da hist&amp;oacute;ria do Met&amp;aacute;fora, quando Dalton Martins enviou uma mensagem para a lista sobre computa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o distribu&amp;iacute;da e Fonseca respondeu: &amp;ldquo;xemeleia a&amp;iacute; que eu n&amp;atilde;o entendi nada&amp;rdquo;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote60sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote60anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;60&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Xemel&amp;ecirc; viria a ser, ali&amp;aacute;s, o nome da segunda lista do Met&amp;aacute;fora, criada em meados de Junho de 2003, quando a primeira lista, alojada no servi&amp;ccedil;o de alojamento eGroups do Yahoo! estava prestes a ultrapassar o limite de armazenamento de &lt;i&gt;emails&lt;/i&gt; - dez mil mensagens - imposto por aquela empresa&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote61sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote61anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;61&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Em pouco mais de um ano, o Met&amp;aacute;fora passou de uma &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;mailing-list&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; a um grupo de ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o para um conceito de colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, uma infra-estrutura ou incubadora para a cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de projectos colaborativos, em que os pr&amp;oacute;prios projectos, como explicou Felipe Fonseca (2003) &amp;ldquo;criam grupos de ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, como se do caos surgisse uma ordem fractal&amp;rdquo;. Ali&amp;aacute;s, um dos termos mais empregues pelos participantes do Met&amp;aacute;fora para definir o processo de funcionamento do projecto era o de &amp;lsquo;caordem&amp;rsquo;, uma mistura de caos com ordem, que nos faz remeter para conceitos como rizoma, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;swarming&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;multid&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; j&amp;aacute; abordados anteriormente&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote62sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote62anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;62&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Outro conceito essencial para compreender o Met&amp;aacute;fora &amp;eacute; o de Intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia Colectiva, introduzido por Pierre L&amp;eacute;vy, segundo o qual estamos a assistir &amp;agrave; emerg&amp;ecirc;ncia de uma nova era do conhecimento que ir&amp;aacute; produzir uma consci&amp;ecirc;ncia humana global&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote63sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote63anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;63&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. No texto de apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote64sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote64anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;64&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; do colectivo, pode-se ler: &amp;ldquo;Met&amp;aacute;fora &amp;eacute; uma intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia colectiva para gerar intelig&amp;ecirc;ncias colectivas. Um projecto aberto de pesquisa e desenvolvimento em diversas &amp;aacute;reas do conhecimento, baseado em algumas premissas do modo de produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;open source&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;.&amp;rdquo; Mais &amp;agrave; frente, verifica-se que o plano de actua&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do projecto passava pela realiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de &amp;ldquo;ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es multiplicadoras de intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia colectiva envolvendo o uso de redes de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;rdquo;. Do mesmo modo, Hernani Dimantas enfatizava essa vis&amp;atilde;o do Met&amp;aacute;fora intelig&amp;ecirc;ncia colectiva num artigo publicado na revista electr&amp;oacute;nica Nova-E ainda durante a fase inicial do projecto&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote65sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote65anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;65&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Os projectos do Met&amp;aacute;fora abrangiam desde solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para acesso &amp;agrave; internet at&amp;eacute; alternativas para estimular o esp&amp;iacute;rito empreendedor das comunidades desfavorecidas. Tais iniciativas estavam baseadas numa organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o conceptual denominada a Tr&amp;iacute;ade da Informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%; widows: 2; orphans: 2;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Infra-estrutura 	f&amp;iacute;sica: computadores pessoais, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;modems&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, 	&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;routers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, 	cabos, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;hubs&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, 	&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;gateways&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;; 	&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%; widows: 2; orphans: 2;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Infra-estrutura 	l&amp;oacute;gica: padr&amp;otilde;es de interliga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, 	sistemas de publica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, 	gest&amp;atilde;o de conhecimento, redes de processamento distribu&amp;iacute;do, 	protocolos; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
