=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de todo o mundo, como o Daypop e o Blogdex, tendo sido ainda divulgado em v&amp;aacute;rios grandes &amp;oacute;rg&amp;atilde;os de comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o social brasileiros como os jornais O Globo e Estado de S. Paulo. Actualmente, o Blogchalking continua a ser empregue por muitos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;bloggers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote73sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote73anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;73&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;P&amp;aacute;dua explicou-nos que se tratou de &amp;quot;uma brincadeira massiva de auto-localiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o geogr&amp;aacute;fica&amp;quot;. Na sua opini&amp;atilde;o, a exposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o alcan&amp;ccedil;ada pelo sistema nos media comerciais ofereceu uma maior visibilidade ao Met&amp;aacute;fora, o que levou a um r&amp;aacute;pido crescimento do n&amp;uacute;mero de assinantes da lista. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Outro membro da lista, Tupi Namba, sugeriu algumas semanas mais tarde, a 24 de Julho, uma deriva&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do projecto, o Blogchalking Reverse&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote74sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote74anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;74&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, que consistia numa tentativa de transpor o sistema de identifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o online de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;bloggers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; para o ambiente &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;offline&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma linguagem de s&amp;iacute;mbolos de giz, tal como o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;Warchalking&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&q