&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Outro projecto que, tal como o Blogchalking, tamb&amp;eacute;m se autonomizou do Met&amp;aacute;fora foi o MetaONG&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote75sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote75anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;75&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;uma comunidade de not&amp;iacute;cias e informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre e para o sector das organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es n&amp;atilde;o-governamentais sem fins lucrativos que surgiu a partir de uma ideia de Felipe Albert&amp;atilde;o&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote76sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote76anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;76&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. O projecto resultou de outra ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do Met&amp;aacute;fora, o MetaComunidade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote77sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote77anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;77&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, iniciada por Felipe Fonseca e que consistiu numa adapta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o para o portugu&amp;ecirc;s do Brasil, tendo em conta as necessidades das comunidades locais do pa&amp;iacute;s, do &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;open-source&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; Drupal de gest&amp;atilde;o e produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de conte&amp;uacute;dos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; que permite um modelo de publica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e edi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o aberta semelhante ao Kuro5hin e ao Digg, onde&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; qualquer utilizador pode submeter not&amp;iacute;cias e outros artigos, que ser&amp;atilde;o moderadas pelos outros utilizadores: as not&amp;iacute;cias v&amp;atilde;o para uma fila e os utilizadores aprovam quais os artigos que ser&amp;atilde;o inclu&amp;iacute;dos na p&amp;aacute;gina inicial e os que s&amp;atilde;o eliminados do arquivo do site. Actualmente (Janeiro de 2006), o site permanece ainda em funcionamento, embora com um n&amp;iacute;vel reduzido de actualiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. No total foram ai publicados at&amp;eacute; hoje 742 textos, encontrando-se estes dividindo nos seguintes assuntos: ambientalismo (56), capta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de recursos (45), cidadania (115), cultura (40), desenvolvimento sustent&amp;aacute;vel (72), ecologia digital (4), empreendedorismo (121), gest&amp;atilde;o (55), inclus&amp;atilde;o digital (92), inform&amp;aacute;tica (12), legisla&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o (7), microcr&amp;eacute;dito (22), pol&amp;iacute;tica (13), sustentabilidade (22) e voluntariado (42).  Not&amp;iacute;cias (184), estudos de caso (146) e artigos (129) s&amp;atilde;o o tipo de conte&amp;uacute;dos mais predominante. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%; widows: 2; orphans: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;A Buzzine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote78sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote78anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;78&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; foi outro projecto criado no seio da &amp;quot;incubadora colaborativa&amp;quot; chamada Met&amp;aacute;fora, segundo a express&amp;atilde;o de Hernani Dimantas (2004), de quem partiu a ideia desta revista electr&amp;oacute;nica. Esta &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;e-zine&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; inspirava-se na &amp;eacute;tica &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;open-source&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e no modelo de neg&amp;oacute;cios introduzido pelo Manifesto Cluetrain, uma das principais refer&amp;ecirc;ncias da nova economia da Internet e outra das grandes influ&amp;ecirc;ncias do Met&amp;aacute;fora&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&q