&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%; widows: 2; orphans: 2;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Um dos projectos do Met&amp;aacute;fora especificamente no dom&amp;iacute;nio da arte e tecnologia foi o Memelab&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote81sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote81anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;81&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, que partiu de uma ideia de Bernardo Schepop. Inicialmente designado de GrafoConexo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote82sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote82anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;82&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; ou MetaMedia Lab, a iniciativa destinava-se &amp;agrave; realiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es art&amp;iacute;sticas e a experimenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es medi&amp;aacute;ticas de forma colaborativa relacionadas com interac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, arte e narrativas n&amp;atilde;o-lineares em ambientes digitais. Como se pode ler no texto de apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dispon&amp;iacute;vel na &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, o Memelab pretendia ser um espa&amp;ccedil;o &amp;quot;aberto &amp;agrave; experimenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; na interac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o homem-m&amp;aacute;quina, indiv&amp;iacute;duo-conhecimento, indiv&amp;iacute;duo-ambiente, indiv&amp;iacute;duo-indiv&amp;iacute;duo, sempre procurando explorar diferentes maneiras de &#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;contar uma hist&amp;oacute;ria&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, seja esta ficcional ou real, individual ou colaborativa&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote83sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote83anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;83&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. O &amp;ecirc;nfase era dado mais uma vez ao &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; livre, a solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es n&amp;atilde;o propriet&amp;aacute;rias e a licen&amp;ccedil;as de autoria semelhantes &amp;agrave; GPL. Todas as obras e interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es elaboradas no &amp;acirc;mbito do Memelab deveriam ser assinadas em nome colectivo dado que &amp;quot;a autoria, no &amp;acirc;mbito art&amp;iacute;stico, tende a uma individualiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da obra, o que n&amp;atilde;o nos interessa&amp;quot;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Este questionamento da conceito de propriedade intelectual est&amp;aacute; bem patente em Wikifiction, uma &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de experimenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es narrativas ficcionais baseado num cen&amp;aacute;rio de fragmenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e de caos semi&amp;oacute;tico que apresentava um modelo semelhante ao colectivo italiano Luther Blissett de produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o descentralizada, onde se tornava imposs&amp;iacute;vel designar o autor de uma ideia e a obra criativa deixava de ser algo est&amp;aacute;vel e perene. Esta &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, contudo, j&amp;aacute; n&amp;atilde;o est&amp;aacute; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote84sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote84anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;84&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Apesar dos planos ambiciosos do Memelab - p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;retendia-se estabelecer uma rede de parcerias com institui&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es estabelecidas e convidar artistas para a elabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de pesquisas e trabalhos comuns -, o projecto n&amp;atilde;o chegou a registar muita actividade, continuando ap&amp;oacute;s o fim do Met&amp;aacute;fora como espa&amp;ccedil;o de alojamento de iniciativas individuais de Schepop e de outros membros do Met&amp;aacute;fora, como o Colectivo de Hist&amp;oacute;rias Digitais de Tatiana Wells, que produz e recolhe narrativas digitais colaborativas de cariz liter&amp;aacute;rio ou jornal&amp;iacute;stico a partir de hist&amp;oacute;rias pessoais elaboradas por jovens da periferia de S&amp;atilde;o Paulo em &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;workshops&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; como os do Autolabs&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote85sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote85anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;85&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: -0.02cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;&quot; class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;Para al&amp;eacute;m destes, o Met&amp;aacute;fora tamb&amp;eacute;m contava com projectos de cariz mais activista, como o Recicle1Pol&amp;iacute;tico&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote86sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote86anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;86&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, uma iniciativa que teve origem numa proposta de Tupi Namba atrav&amp;eacute;s de uma  mensagem enviada para a lista Met&amp;aacute;fora a 2 de Outubro e visava alertar para a polui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o visual gerada pela propaganda pol&amp;iacute;tica e para o desperd&amp;iacute;cio que esta representava atrav&amp;eacute;s da recolha dos cartazes, faixas, panfletos e outro &amp;lsquo;lixo&amp;rsquo; composto de material imperme&amp;aacute;vel e n&amp;atilde;o-biodegrad&amp;aacute;vel deixado pelas ruas das cidades nas v&amp;eacute;speras das elei&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es presidenciais brasileiras de Outubro e Novembro de 2002. Depois de recortado, o material seria reciclado e reaproveitado, transformando-o em arte urbana, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;land art&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; e instala&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de arquitectura n&amp;oacute;mada como um circo, m&amp;aacute;scaras, um acampamento para os sem-terra, cabanas para os sem-abrigo, toldos para bailes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;funk,&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; concertos de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;hip-hop&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;, mo&amp;iacute;nhos de vento, entre outros objectos. Este tipo de zonas tempor&amp;aacute;rias aut&amp;oacute;nomas (TAZs) decorreram em S&amp;atilde;o Paulo e Belo Horizonte&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote87sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote87anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;87&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Nesta &amp;uacute;ltima cidade, o Recicle1Pol&amp;iacute;tico terminou com uma interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o no &amp;acirc;mbito do evento ProvOs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote88sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote88anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;88&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt; de Novembro de 2002, coordenado por Daniel P&amp;aacute;dua e Adriana Veloso &amp;ndash; que tamb&amp;eacute;m fazia parte do Metaf&amp;oacute;ra. Este festival, o primeiro de media t&amp;aacute;cticos no Brasil, abrangeu um conjunto de ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es descentralizadas semelhantes a TAZs visando a democratiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e do acesso aos media&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote89sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote89anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;89&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;. Numa ac&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de reciclagem de cartazes, o colectivo art&amp;iacute;stico local Ren&amp;uacute;ncia realizou uma instala&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o denominada &amp;ldquo;Argumentos&amp;rdquo; no edif&amp;iacute;cio que alojava o evento&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote90sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote90anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;90&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, enquanto que o artista pl&amp;aacute;stico Andr&amp;eacute; construiu m&amp;aacute;scaras com mensagens de cr&amp;iacute;tica social a partir de autocolantes dos candidatos eleitorais&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote91sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote91anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;91&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Apesar do fim do Met&amp;aacute;fora, o Recicle1Pol&amp;iacute;tico foi retomado em Agosto de 2004 pelo movimento Midia Tatica Brasil&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote92sym&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote92anc&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnoteanc&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;92&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  &lt;/sp