&lt;div id=&quot;sdfootnote25&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote25anc&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote25sym&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnotesym&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;25&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;&quot;&gt;Sch&amp;uuml;tze 	(2000)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;&quot;&gt;. 	Este autor vislumbra uma liga&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre as pr&amp;aacute;ticas 	antropof&amp;aacute;gicas e as t&amp;aacute;cticas de incorpora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o 	paras&amp;iacute;tica de alguns projectos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;&quot;&gt;artivistas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;pt-PT&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;&quot;&gt; 	como a RTMark, Mongrel (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mongrelx.org&quot; title=&quot;www.mongrelx.org&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;www.mongrelx.org&lt;/a&gt;), JODI (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jodi.org&quot; title=&quot;www.jodi.org&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;www.jodi.org&lt;/a&gt;), 	m9ndfukc (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.m9ndfukc.org&quot; title=&quot;www.m9ndfukc.org&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;www.m9ndfukc.org&lt;/a&gt;) e Shredder (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.potatoland.org/shredder&quot; title=&quot;www.potatoland.org/shredder&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;www.potatoland.org/shredder&lt;/a&gt;) 	de Mark Napier.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;sdfootnote26&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote26anc&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote26sym&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnotesym&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;26&lt;/a&gt;Esta 	met&amp;aacute;fora seria tamb&amp;eacute;m adoptada pelo Tropicalismo, o 	movimento de m&amp;uacute;sica popular brasileira do final dos anos 60 	representado por Caetano Veloso e Gilberto Gil, entre outros, que 	efectuaram uma fus&amp;atilde;o do samba com a contra-cultura e a m&amp;uacute;sica 	&lt;i&gt;Pop e Rock&lt;/i&gt; da altura, como se pode ler no site do Digitofagia 	e no texto de Felipe Fonseca (2005).&lt;/p&gt;
