&lt;div id=&quot;sdfootnote41&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote41anc&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote41sym&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnotesym&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;41&lt;/a&gt;Ver 	arquivo das emiss&amp;otilde;es em 	&lt;a href=&quot;http://ftaaimc.org/or/static/radio_en.shtml&quot; title=&quot;http://ftaaimc.org/or/static/radio_en.shtml&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://ftaaimc.org/or/static/radio_en.shtml&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
