&lt;p class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote73anc&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote73sym&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnotesym&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;73&lt;/a&gt;Uma 	pesquisa pelo termo &amp;quot;blogchalk&amp;quot; efectuada a 23 de Janeiro 	de 2006 no Google indicava 514 mil resultados.&lt;/p&gt;
