&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;sdfootnote84&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote84anc&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote84sym&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnotesym&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;84&lt;/a&gt;P&amp;aacute;gina 	do projecto na &lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt; do Met&amp;aacute;fora dispon&amp;iacute;vel em 	&lt;a href=&quot;http://ogum.metareciclagem.org/metafora/wiki/index.php?WikiFiction&quot; title=&quot;http://ogum.metareciclagem.org/metafora/wiki/index.php?WikiFiction&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://ogum.metareciclagem.org/metafora/wiki/index.php?WikiFiction&lt;/a&gt;. 	Ver c&amp;oacute;pia de arquivo da &lt;i&gt;wiki&lt;/i&gt; em 	&lt;a href=&quot;http://web.archive.org/web/20030813055806/wikifiction.memelab.org/HomePage&quot; title=&quot;http://web.archive.org/web/20030813055806/wikifiction.memelab.org/HomePage&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://web.archive.org/web/20030813055806/wikifiction.memelab.org/HomePage&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
