&lt;div id=&quot;sdfootnote125&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;sdfootnote-western&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#sdfootnote125anc&quot; name=&quot;sdfootnote125sym&quot; class=&quot;sdfootnotesym&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;125&lt;/a&gt;Em 	Mar&amp;ccedil;o de 2003 viria a ser implementado um sistema de 	comunidade &lt;i&gt;online&lt;/i&gt; baseado na plataforma Drupal de forma a dar 	resposta a essa necessidade de uma maior comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o 	interna e externa. Este sistema, integrado no site do Met&amp;aacute;fora, 	j&amp;aacute; n&amp;atilde;o se encontra dispon&amp;iacute;vel. Ver c&amp;oacute;pia 	de arquivo em 	&lt;a href=&quot;http://web.archive.org/web/20031022213440/http://drupal.projetometafora.org/&quot; title=&quot;http://web.archive.org/web/20031022213440/http://drupal.projetometafora.org/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://web.archive.org/web/20031022213440/http://drupal.projetometafora....&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
